text: Morrison Hotel is the fifth studio album by American hard rock band The Doors. It was released on 9 February, 1970 through Elektra Records and went to number 4 in the United States, number 6 in the Netherlands and number 12 in the United Kingdom. == Track listing == ===Original album=== Details are taken from the 1970 Elektra Records album and may differ from other sources. ===Reissues=== == References == Category:1970 albums Category:The Doors albums
title: Morrison Hotel
